commit cc6ea51b431618a86fd4987affc16aaf158ebb24
Author: Mattt <mattt@me.com>
Date:   Mon Feb 23 13:34:29 2026 -0800

    Add cache-first snapshot download paths with resume and local-only fallback (#34)
    
    * Add cache-first snapshot download paths with resume and local-only fallback
    
    * Rename parameter to useSnapshotCachePath
    
    * Incorporate feedback from review
    
    * Incorporate feedback from review
    
    * Consolidate path validation logic into HubCache
    
    * Prevent overlapping resume range requests across concurrent blob downloads
    
    * Add documentation for new parameters
    
    * Refactor downloadSnapshot method to be separate overloads instead of having useSnapshotCachePath parameter
    
    * Incorporate feedback from review

