commit 7edf91e7408565d717e25d9c799ab69877cfde43
Author: Mattt <mattt@me.com>
Date:   Mon Feb 23 06:14:26 2026 -0800

    Return cache-backed snapshot paths and add commit-hash metadata fast path (#33)
    
    * Return snapshot cache paths and skip commit API calls for complete cached snapshots
    
    * Add HubCacheError case for when cached path resolution fails
    
    * Skip FileOperationTests on Linux
    
    MockURLProtocol is unreliable, even when running tests serially
    
    * Incorporate feedback from review

